title: No Bake Chocolate (Coconut) Cookies
date: 2021-04-21
category: dessert
tags: fudgy
---

## Ingredients
* 3 cups quick cooking oats
* 1 cup sweetened flaked coconut
* 2 cups white sugar
* ½ cup unsweetened cocoa powder
* ½ cup milk
* ½ cup margarine

## Instructions
1. Line a baking sheet with waxed paper.
1. Mix oats and coconut in a large bowl until thoroughly combined.
1. Stir sugar, cocoa powder, milk, and margarine together in a saucepan over medium heat until the mixture is smooth. 
1. Bring to a boil and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly. Pour over the oats & coconut, and quickly mix to coat. 
1. Drop by tablespoon onto prepared baking sheet; let cookies cool and harden.
1. Store in an airtight container.

